ime-with-the-datetimepicker-control.md)  \n Shows steps to for a `DateTimePicker` to display times only.  \n  \n## Reference  \n <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DateTimePicker>  \n Describes this class and has links to all its members.  \n  \n <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar>  \n Describes this class and has links to all its members.  \n  \n## Related Sections  \n [Controls to Use on Windows Forms](../../../../docs/framework/winforms/controls/controls-to-use-on-windows-forms.md)  \n Provides a complete list of Windows Forms controls, with links to information on their use.  \n  \n [MonthCalendar Control](../../../../docs/framework/winforms/controls/monthcalendar-control-windows-forms.md)  \n Presents an intuitive graphical interface for users to view and set date information.","nodes":[{"pos":[12,67],"content":"DateTimePicker Control (Windows Forms) | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"DateTimePicker Control (Windows Forms) | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,55]}]},{"pos":[578,616],"content":"DateTimePicker Control (Windows Forms)","linkify":"DateTimePicker Control (Windows Forms)","nodes":[{"content":"DateTimePicker Control (Windows Forms)","pos":[0,38]}]},{"content":"The Windows Forms <ph id=\"ph1\">`DateTimePicker`</ph> control allows the user to select a single item from a list of dates or times.","pos":[617,730],"source":"The Windows Forms `DateTimePicker` control allows the user to select a single item from a list of dates or times."},{"content":"When used to represent a date, it appears in two parts: a drop-down list with a date represented in text, and a grid that appears when you click on the down-arrow next to the list.","pos":[731,911]},{"pos":[920,935],"content":"In This Section","linkify":"In This Section","nodes":[{"content":"In This Section","pos":[0,15]}]},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>DateTimePicker Control Overview<ept id=\"p1\">](../../../../docs/framework/winforms/controls/datetimepicker-control-overview-wind